column5: Spring is coming Spring is coming Spring is coming Spring is coming.......  At least that's what I keep telling myself!!!  Great report Glen...thanks for the pics and the painful reminder that it's still cold here....LOL
Nice haul........looks cold for there? A sweater AND a jacket........?  You sure get some nice slabs down there!!  Thanks for the report, Sinker
*Drooling*  Only 57 more sleeps until Crappie opens!!!!
Can't type what I really want to say  Good report Glen glad to see ya catching  Thanks for sharing
Thanks for the report Glen. You certainly got a good whack of fish there. I especially like the one dated Feb 28 2008.  Good on ya, Gen'ral!
Thanks Glen! Open water looks so much better than ice! Nice fesh!
Good thing you fished yesterday glen, if it was today  you would be waiting 4 more years to have the same luck you might have had today, go figure
Nice going there Glen! Glad to see your getting out... how long till ya loose the jacket?
Great pics GCD.  Always admire your soft-water reports.  I'm with Cliff...  Spring is coming!!!!! Spring is coming!!!!! Spring is coming!!!!! Spring is coming!!!!!   reefrunner
Thats pretty sweet!I dont think I would eat anything other Crappie and crawfish if I was to move down there. Joe
Now that's just plain Mean G!!!  Here we got another blizzard with wind howling and you're out there catching fish in a boat with a light jacket on.  Its enough to make a grown woman cry  Joey
Not from Zone 16 - 17 - 18  Cheers  David  aka Superdad
Some would argue a different planet altogether!
I was thinkin we had a member by the name of that "zone"!
